## Error Messages

All errors actionable, following goloo patterns:

```go
var (
    ErrLibvirtMissing      = errors.New("virsh not found: install libvirt (apt install libvirt-daemon-system)")
    ErrVirtInstallMissing  = errors.New("virt-install not found: install virtinst (apt install virtinst)")
    ErrGenISOmissing       = errors.New("neither cloud-localds nor genisoimage found: install cloud-image-utils or genisoimage")
    ErrImageDownloadFailed = errors.New("failed to download cloud image: check network and retry")
    ErrNoIP                = errors.New("VM started but no IP assigned within 60s: check libvirt network with 'virsh net-list'")
    ErrDomainExists        = errors.New("VM already exists: destroy first with 'govirt destroy <name>'")
    ErrDomainNotFound      = errors.New("VM not found: check 'govirt list' for available VMs")
    ErrKVMUnavailable      = errors.New("KVM not available: check /dev/kvm exists and current user is in 'kvm' group")
)
```

