## Prerequisites Check

On `govirt create` (local), check before proceeding:

1. `/dev/kvm` exists (KVM available)
2. `virsh` is in PATH
3. `virt-install` is in PATH
4. At least one of `cloud-localds` or `genisoimage` is in PATH
5. Current user can connect to `qemu:///system` (or `LIBVIRT_DEFAULT_URI`)

If any check fails, print a clear error with the install command.

