## Simultaneous Deployments

Identical to goloo: separate `local`, `aws`, and `do` state sections allow one config to have active deployments on multiple providers simultaneously:

```json
{
  "vm": { ... },
  "local": { "ip": "192.168.122.5", "domain_name": "web-server", ... },
  "aws":   { "public_ip": "54.1.2.3", ... },
  "do":    { "public_ip": "192.241.0.1", ... }
}
```

Delete each independently:
```bash
govirt destroy web-server --local
govirt destroy web-server --aws
govirt destroy web-server --do
```

