### Phase 4: Image Manager
- Implement `internal/images/manager.go`:
  - Map image shorthand to download URL
  - Download with progress reporting
  - Verify SHA256 if checksum file is available
  - Cache in `$GOVIRT_IMAGE_CACHE`
  - Return path to cached image

### Phase 5: LibvirtProvider
- Implement `internal/provider/libvirt/`:
  - `virsh.go`: wrappers for `virsh` commands (list, dominfo, domifaddr, destroy, undefine, start, shutdown)
  - `iso.go`: generate NoCloud cloud-init ISO via `cloud-localds` or `genisoimage`
  - `network.go`: IP detection via `virsh domifaddr`, DHCP lease fallback
  - `libvirt.go`: main `Provider` struct implementing `VMProvider` interface
- Unit tests for command building and output parsing

### Phase 6: CLI
- Copy `cmd/goloo/main.go` from goloo
- Replace all `multipass.New()` with `libvirt.New()`
- Update provider names ("multipass" в†’ "libvirt")
- Update binary name to `govirt`
- Update stack folder default from `~/.config/goloo` to `~/.config/govirt`
- Update environment variable prefix from `GOLOO_` to `GOVIRT_`
- Update /etc/hosts marker from `goloo:` to `govirt:`
- Update help text and error messages

### Phase 7: Cloud Providers
- Copy `internal/provider/aws/` from goloo verbatim (no changes)
- Copy `internal/provider/digitalocean/` from goloo verbatim (no changes)
- Wire into `getProvider()` in CLI

### Phase 8: Integration and Polish
- End-to-end tests against real libvirt
- Error message review
