## Key Differences from goloo (Summary)

| Aspect | goloo | govirt |
|--------|-------|--------|
| Local backend | Multipass | libvirt + virt-install + KVM |
| Local VM tool | `multipass launch` | `virt-install --import` |
| cloud-init delivery | Multipass native | NoCloud ISO (second disk) |
| Image management | Multipass auto-downloads | govirt downloads qcow2 to `~/.cache/govirt/images` |
| Host mounts | `multipass mount` | virtiofs (or 9p fallback) |
| SSH to local VM | `multipass shell <name>` | `ssh ubuntu@<ip>` |
| IP detection | `multipass info --format json` | `virsh domifaddr` |
| Stop/Start | `multipass stop/start` | `virsh shutdown` / `virsh start` |
| List | `multipass list --format json` | `virsh list --all` |
| Delete | `multipass delete && purge` | `virsh destroy && undefine --remove-all-storage` |
| State fields | `local.ip` | `local.ip` + `local.domain_name` + `local.disk_path` + `local.cloud_init_iso` + `local.network` |
| Config dir | `~/.config/goloo` | `~/.config/govirt` |
| Env var prefix | `GOLOO_` | `GOVIRT_` |
| /etc/hosts marker | `# goloo:<name>` | `# govirt:<name>` |
| AWS provider | unchanged | unchanged |
| DigitalOcean provider | unchanged | unchanged |
| cloud-init processing | unchanged | unchanged + mount injection |
| Config schema | `LocalState{IP, HostsEntry}` | `LocalState{IP, HostsEntry, DomainName, DiskPath, CloudInitISO, Network}` |
